she made at Light Strokes,

383
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:05,119
imitating my work.

384
00:17:06,799 --> 00:17:08,240
Light Strokes displays my photos

385
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:09,319
and I know the owner.

386
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,200
So you think

387
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:12,039
I know her?

388
00:17:13,039 --> 00:17:13,960
Then,

389
00:17:14,119 --> 00:17:15,079
my studio's fire

390
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,799
happened around

391
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:18,880
the same time as her disappearance.

392
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:20,240
So you think

393
00:17:20,279 --> 00:17:21,119
her disappearance

394
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:22,480
is connected to me?

395
00:17:26,839 --> 00:17:28,039
Let's say,

396
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:30,119
you think

397
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,319
I'm the murderer?

398
00:17:33,359 --> 00:17:34,839
I killed Wei

399
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:36,519
and set the fire

400
00:17:36,599 --> 00:17:38,119
to burn down my own studio

401
00:17:38,599 --> 00:17:39,680
to ruin evidence?

402
00:17:41,079 --> 00:17:41,839
Is it

403
00:17:42,799 --> 00:17:44,119
what you call

404
00:17:45,279 --> 00:17:46,480
The Logic Behind Truth?

405
00:17:55,799 --> 00:17:56,720
Behind art

406
00:17:57,559 --> 00:17:58,839
lies inspiration and dedication.

407
00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:00,319
The Logic Behind Art.

408
00:18:00,319 --> 00:18:01,240
This title sounds

409
00:18:01,279 --> 00:18:03,079
too sensationalistic.

410
00:18:05,119 --> 00:18:07,000
And you only have 100,000 followers.

411
00:18:07,400 --> 00:18:09,240
Are you just out of content ideas

412
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:12,039
and here to pick a fight?

413
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:14,799
To be honest,

414
00:18:15,519 --> 00:18:16,319
I don't understand

415
00:18:16,319 --> 00:18:17,640
your analysis narratives,

416
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,759
but I at least know common sense.

417
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,079
My studio caught fire

418
00:18:21,119 --> 00:18:22,640
last year in November.

419
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:24,480
Today is September 30.

420
00:18:24,839 --> 00:18:25,839
It's been almost a year.

421
00:18:26,440 --> 00:18:27,720
She disappeared a year ago.

422
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:28,920
Yet you come

423
00:18:29,680 --> 00:18:30,799
to me now?

424
00:18:32,359 --> 00:18:33,200
Besides,

425
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:35,799
are you a police officer?

426
00:18:38,400 --> 00:18:39,680
The materials used

427
00:18:39,759 --> 00:18:40,240
for this...

428
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:41,480
Kaolin clay.

429
00:18:42,039 --> 00:18:42,720
Clear glaze.

430
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,240
The same as Light Strokes'.

431
00:18:44,279 --> 00:18:45,359
We use the same

432
00:18:45,359 --> 00:18:46,319
raw material supplier.

433
00:18:47,079 --> 00:18:49,119
Most ceramic artists

434
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:50,119
in Caorong City

435
00:18:50,359 --> 00:18:51,960
use similar materials.

436
00:18:52,680 --> 00:18:54,759
It's like every restaurant

437
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:56,799
serves plain rice.

438
00:18:58,680 --> 00:19:00,200
This plate has blemish flaws.

439
00:19:03,359 --> 00:19:04,640
You've studied ceramics?

440
00:19:05,440 --> 00:19:06,440
Actually, blemish flaws

441
00:19:06,799 --> 00:19:08,079
are common

442
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,440
for beginners.

443
00:19:09,599 --> 00:19:10,799
Use this plate as an example.

444
00:19:11,519 --> 00:19:12,319
Its wheel throwing

445
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:13,079
and coloring

446
00:19:13,640 --> 00:19:14,440
are both subpar.

447
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:16,440
So the blemish flaws

448
00:19:16,920 --> 00:19:17,839
don't matter here.

449
00:19:25,839 --> 00:19:26,680
Mr. Big Hui,

450
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:29,160
I think we could

451
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:30,279
end this conversation.

452
00:19:30,759 --> 00:19:33,000
For both of us,

453
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:34,119
(this is)

454
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:35,519
(a completely meaningless)

455
00:19:35,559 --> 00:19:36,759
(and useless conversation.)

456
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,720
(I don't understand your work.)

457
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:07,720
(Interesting?)

458
00:20:09,799 --> 00:20:10,640
Not really.

459
00:20:11,319 --> 00:20:12,400
I just don't have a choice.

460
00:20:13,359 --> 00:20:14,279
Because

461
00:20:14,559 --> 00:20:16,359
I don't want to get a low-paid,

462
00:20:16,799 --> 00:20:18,160
regular work,

463
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:20,599
or overwhelmed by high-paid work.

464
00:20:21,799 --> 00:20:22,720
I don't want

465
00:20:23,279 --> 00:20:24,359
to marry rich

466
00:20:24,559 --> 00:20:25,920
and live a dependent life.

467
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:28,119
I don't wake up early.

468
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:29,408
I love staying up late.

469
00:20:29,759 --> 00:20:30,519
I don't want to

470
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:32,279
work hard or slack off.

471
00:20:32,759 --> 00:20:33,599
Livestreaming

472
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:34,519
and making videos

473
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:36,599
are just ways I escape reality.

474
00:20:37,480 --> 00:20:38,200
Of course,

475
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:40,279
I fantasize that someday

476
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:42,519
I might go viral,

477
00:20:42,599 --> 00:20:44,039
earning quite a fortune.

478
00:20:45,039 --> 00:20:46,759
If I had a fortune,

479
00:20:47,039 --> 00:20:48,200
I could stop panicking

480
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:48,920
or worrying

481
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:49,880
for a while.

482
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:52,359
Then I could really think about

483
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:55,200
how to

484
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:57,240
completely

485
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:59,000
transform myself.

486
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:00,599
How?

487
00:21:02,319 --> 00:21:03,119
No idea yet.

488
00:21:04,079 --> 00:21:04,880
People like me

489
00:21:05,359 --> 00:21:06,240
are just worthless.

490
00:21:09,039 --> 00:21:10,079
But you

491
00:21:10,519 --> 00:21:11,640
make me believe

492
00:21:12,440 --> 00:21:14,119
that someone like me
can be extraordinary.

493
00:21:15,240 --> 00:21:16,559
So is your boyfriend?

494
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:19,079
Ex-boyfriend.

495
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:22,279
He's a video creator.

496
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:23,559
He works hard,

497
00:21:23,799 --> 00:21:25,200
collecting material, editing,

498
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:26,599
even composing original scores.

499
00:21:27,359 --> 00:21:28,200
He keeps updating

500
00:21:28,359 --> 00:21:29,559
and accumulating fans.

501
00:21:30,480 --> 00:21:31,400
But it's useless.

502
00:21:31,920 --> 00:21:33,119
There's no hope in sight.

503
00:21:33,839 --> 00:21:34,759
What kind of videos?

504
00:21:35,200 --> 00:21:36,759
The Logic Behind Truth.

505
00:21:37,519 --> 00:21:38,839
Who can see the truth clearly?

506
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:40,440
Who cares about the logic?

507
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:45,559
(October 21)
It's past midnight.

508
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:47,440
Want me to stay

509
00:21:48,119 --> 00:21:49,599
or leave?

510
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,119
I want you to stay.

511
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:57,119
And

512
00:21:58,799 --> 00:22:00,200
you've never been worthless.

513
00:22:01,839 --> 00:22:03,559
A charming man like you

514
00:22:04,119 --> 00:22:05,920
must attract many women.

515
00:22:06,519 --> 00:22:07,200
And many women

516
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:08,440
would fall for you.

517
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:10,640
Them and me,

518
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:12,319
what's the difference?

519
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:14,559
You're different.

520
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:16,599
Believe it or not,

521
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:18,240
but I really think

522
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:20,599
you understand me.

523
00:22:21,240 --> 00:22:22,640
Many things you do

524
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:24,480
are what I wish you'd do.

525
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:26,440
Many things you say

526
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:27,680
are what I want to hear.

527
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:29,960
This is rare.

528
00:22:31,559 --> 00:22:32,359
Soulmate?

529
00:22:32,799 --> 00:22:34,000
I dislike that term.

530
00:22:34,319 --> 00:22:35,480
But it's exactly what it is.

531
00:22:36,599 --> 00:22:38,200
What if I pretended to be the version

532
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:39,480
you like

533
00:22:39,759 --> 00:22:40,960
just to get close to you?

534
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:43,119
How is that possible?

535
00:22:45,720 --> 00:22:46,960
How could you possibly know

536
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:49,039
what kind of person I like?

537
00:22:51,279 --> 00:22:51,960
It seems

538
00:22:52,559 --> 00:22:53,759
she truly gets you.

539
00:22:54,359 --> 00:22:55,240
What did you say?

540
00:22:57,319 --> 00:22:58,079
You know what?

541
00:22:58,799 --> 00:22:59,880
I've fallen for you.

542
00:23:00,119 --> 00:23:01,039
It seems I'm destined

543
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:02,319
to fall for you.

544
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:03,720
Though

545
00:23:04,359 --> 00:23:05,079
I know

546
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:06,559
you're not a good man.

547
00:23:11,119 --> 00:23:12,400
How am I not one then?

548
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:14,880
You

549
00:23:17,119 --> 00:23:18,240
certainly aren't.

550
00:23:26,944 --> 00:23:28,759
(Part-time Worker L)

551
00:23:28,759 --> 00:23:29,240
Say it.

552
00:23:29,559 --> 00:23:30,640
As you say,

553
00:23:30,960 --> 00:23:31,960
I met your husband.

554
00:23:32,240 --> 00:23:32,960
Just do things

555
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:34,000
as I instructed.

556
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:35,880
No need to update me on the details.

557
00:23:37,359 --> 00:23:38,319
Don't want to hear it?

558
00:23:38,759 --> 00:23:39,279
Fine.

559
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:41,119
After it's done,

560
00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:42,960
I'll give you a full report.

561
00:23:43,079 --> 00:23:44,319
You'd better hurry.

562
00:23:44,799 --> 00:23:45,759
Don't drag it out.

563
00:23:46,079 --> 00:23:47,079
Don't worry.

564
00:23:47,480 --> 00:23:48,279
Maybe

565
00:23:48,799 --> 00:23:50,680
your husband is more impatient than you.

566
00:23:57,440 --> 00:23:58,480
I can't help you

567
00:23:59,079 --> 00:23:59,880
with evidence.

568
00:24:00,839 --> 00:24:02,640
I know a lawyer in this area.

569
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:05,359
You can try consulting him.

570
00:24:13,696 --> 00:24:15,584
(Calling...)

571
00:24:18,400 --> 00:24:19,039
Hello.

572
00:24:20,480 --> 00:24:21,599
Zhang Ye recommended you.

573
00:24:22,720 --> 00:24:23,480
Zhang Ye?

574
00:24:24,119 --> 00:24:24,839
Got it.

575
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:25,839
Divorce lawsuit?

576
00:24:26,160 --> 00:24:26,839
What's your name?

577
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:29,759
Hello.

578
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:30,839
Say something.

579
00:24:31,359 --> 00:24:32,200
Don't be shy.

580
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:33,680
Investigate your husband?

581
00:24:44,039 --> 00:24:44,839
I think

582
00:24:45,039 --> 00:24:46,759
I should lower my hand.

583
00:24:52,279 --> 00:24:52,920
Take a break.

584
00:24:57,880 --> 00:24:58,880
What can I do?

585
00:25:00,839 --> 00:25:02,000
My company's annual gala

586
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,920
requires all partners

587
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,640
to perform something.

588
00:25:06,599 --> 00:25:07,720
So I hired

589
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:08,839
a tutor.

590
00:25:09,079 --> 00:25:10,160
I come here every day.

591
00:25:10,720 --> 00:25:11,400
Take a seat.

592
00:25:12,079 --> 00:25:13,039
Just say it.

593
00:25:15,000 --> 00:25:16,240
You called

594
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:18,000
the person I recommended,

595
00:25:18,200 --> 00:25:19,319
but hung up without saying

596
00:25:19,319 --> 00:25:19,880
anything.

597
00:25:20,079 --> 00:25:21,200
He asked me

598
00:25:21,359 --> 00:25:22,039
what's going on.

599
00:25:22,519 --> 00:25:23,960
That's it?

600
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:26,000
Sorry for troubling you.

601
00:25:27,839 --> 00:25:28,559
Two things.

602
00:25:30,240 --> 00:25:31,240
First,

603
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:34,240
it's a coincidence.

604
00:25:35,000 --> 00:25:36,519
I searched online for your husband.

605
00:25:38,000 --> 00:25:39,079
Want

606
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:40,359
